1. Make sure the 'sinatra' gem is installed.
2. From the command line, you can start the server by 'ruby main.rb'
3. Go to your web browser and go to the localhost port that is listed in command line
4. If you have the 'shotgun' gem installed, you can instead run 'shotgun main.rb'
5. ctrl+c to stop the server

Check out the deployed version on Heroku:
http://evening-river-8201.herokuapp.com/
